
BUFFERS

:buffers - list all buffers and some info

nav
:buffer ID
:bn - next buffer
:bp
:bf - first
:bl

Ctrl ^ - alt buffer


:badd filename - create buffer
:bdelete id or name - del

:%bdelete - delete all buffers

WINDOWS

Ctrl W s - horz split
Ctrl W v - vertical split
Ctrl W n - new file
buffer id  Ctrl W ^ - 

navigate via ctrl w and arrows

jumplist

positions are svaed

:jumps - display jumps
ctrl o - prev cursor pos 
ctrl i - next cursor pos

change list

insert mode

g; next change
g, prev change
